hu.kazocsaba.math.matrix.backbone

Class Vector3Op

  • java.lang.Object
    • hu.kazocsaba.math.matrix.backbone.MatrixOp
      • hu.kazocsaba.math.matrix.backbone.VectorOp
        • hu.kazocsaba.math.matrix.backbone.Vector3Op

  • public final class Vector3Op
extends VectorOp
    Implementations of the Vector3 functions for the benefit of Vector subclasses. These methods rely on the Matrix.get(int, int), Matrix.set(int, int, double), Matrix.getRowCount(), and Matrix.getColumnCount() functions, so all others can delegate to this class.
    Author:
    Kaz√≥ Csaba
